data.description: NEW PRICE! Welcome to 390 Ranch Rd! This charming property offers the perfect blend of convenience and comfort. Located just minutes away from Health Care Facilities and Schools, this home boasts a prime location that's ideal for those seeking easy access to essential amenities. RV enthusiasts will be delighted by the dedicated RV Parking with an Electrical Hookup, making it effortless to explore and embark on adventures while keeping your vehicle ready for the road. The fenced back yard is a haven for relaxation and entertainment. The spacious deck provides an inviting space to host gatherings, enjoy outdoor meals, or simply unwind while taking in the serene surroundings. Inside, discover a thoughtfully designed layout featuring 3 bedrooms, ensuring ample space for your family or guests. The well-appointed 1 bathroom caters to your daily needs with modern convenience. The living room and family room offer versatility and space for everyone to find their favorite spot. Stay warm and cozy during colder months thanks to the delightful pellet stove, creating an inviting atmosphere that truly feels like home. Don't miss the opportunity to make 390 Ranch Rd your new address. Experience the benefits of an excellent location, versatile living spaces, and outdoor amenities that cater to your lifestyle. Schedule a viewing today and envision the possibilities that await! Main Listing Agent is related to Sellers.
